data.description: You don't have to settle. You can have it all. An outstanding home in a vibrant, mature neighborhood, nestled in the foothills of Piestewa Peak, near enough to the freeway and main arteries to get around the Valley but far enough for peace and comfort. The present owners enjoy the quick drive downtown for sports, theater, and entertainment, as well as close proximity to several hiking trailheads and lots of dining options. They enjoy entertaining guests in their private backyard, catching incredible sunsets, and enjoying the breathtaking mountain and city views with neighbors, family, and friends on the view deck. An out-of-state move prompts the sale of their home.
